==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Deliciousness
<hw>De*li"cious*ness</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>The quality of
being delicious; <as>as, the <ex>deliciousness</ex> of a
repast</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Luxury.</def> ⟦ldquo⟧To drive away all superfluity
and <xex>deliciousness</xex>.⟦rdquo⟧ <rj><au>Sir T. North.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Delict</ent>⟦br⟧
